window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Dean Silver. Wildcard. Kidnapper.</b></p> <p>The last one hasn’t led me into hot water just yet, but it’s only a matter of time. Capturing the formerly super-powered diva known as Phenomenon has set the clock to ticking.</p> <p>Before it runs out, I need to figure out what to do with her. She has knowledge far beyond anything my team has, and I want her to help me.</p> <p>The question is: will she do it?</p> <p>If she doesn’t, Unity might just find themselves destroyed before they barely had the chance to shine.</p>"; 
